inc in chicago 
baker was even more blunt 
theres nothing but dark clouds he said noting that 
preliminary economic indicators released this month indicate that 
the august number was not a onemonth phenomenon the picture 
im getting is that this is a longterm trend 
the drop in the index designed to forecast activity six to nine 
months ahead was the sharpest since a 14 percent decline in the 
month after the oct 19 1987 stock market crash when the dow 
