began monday two traffickers were killed and several wounded 
police said at least 70 people were arrested including carmelo 
meco dominguez the reputed head of the smashed drug network 
dominguez 34 considered one of bolivias top three drug 
traffickers handled five to 10 tons of pure cocaine a month much 
of it bound for the us market law enforcement agents said 
we have destroyed one of the top trafficking operations in 
bolivia and south america ferrarone said he said the network 
shipped cocaine to colombia and to mexico and had strong ties to 
colombias medellin and cali cartels 
