per l00 pounds from a revised august average of 1430 per 
hundredweight that was up 40 cents from september 1989 
vegetable prices dropped 58 percent from august and were down 
15 percent from a year earlier tomatoes led the september 
declines 
fruit prices rose 8 percent from august and were up 15 percent 
from a year ago apples led september gain followed by oranges and 
grapefruit 
the report said 
