agreed to turn the matter over to staff and schedule another public 
conference tuesday 
aside from the motor vehicle section of the bill the conferees 
must still tackle sections dealing with acid rain controls toxic 
chemical emissions from industrial plants requirements on the use 
of cleaner gasoline blends in some urban areas and whether to 
provide assistance to workers who lose their jobs because of 
tougher pollution control requirements 
